data.description: Spacious & gracious gem with 2492 living area featuring 2 large master suites on an oversized .45 Acre lot! Upgrades include new 2022 main house AC and new generator w/500-gal underground gas tank, in 2023 new LVP flooring in sunroom/den, guest bedroom & laundry room, beautiful new carpet in both master bedrooms & spacious living room, new interior/exterior paint, new hot water heater, disposal, exterior lighting & railings on all decks, new front & rear gutters, new front yard irrigation, sod & mulch. The great room features a custom entertainment center, soaring ceilings with beautiful wood beams & coral wall wood-burning fireplace overlooking the open kitchen & dining areas. 1st large master suite offers 2 large walk-in closets with an oversized master bathroom, 2nd spacious and cheerful master suite offers custom shutters, ensuite bathroom & large walk-in closet. This is a wonderful value for a large, move-in ready home within minutes to Sanibel! McGregor Woods offers heated pool & spa, tennis, pickle ball, fishing pier & clubhouse with HOA fees of only $425/quarter! Come see this spacious beauty & fall in love with your new SW Florida home!
